{"tid":992087,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［都市傳說］30日對鏡子問：你是誰？","createTime":"2019-01-23T01:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T09:45:00.000Z","uid":130976,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"82a9c4d467864b19e893acbeb00baa4617fe7d1a","tid":992087,"uid":130976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Od32b8r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOd32b8r.png&h=4c7b794a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《都市傳說》連續30天 對著鏡子問你是誰...會...<br />\n大家有聽過格式塔崩壞實驗嗎？這個實驗就是讓一個人，每天都對著鏡子裡的自己問『你是誰』，一天一次，但是每一次都要反覆問10次，持續30天，據說這會讓一個人崩潰...<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L832b8Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL832b8Y.png&h=0736ac1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而究竟什麼麼是格式塔崩壞呢？簡單的解釋跟舉例。就是當人一直在注視一個常看到的文字幾十秒之後（或者是短 時間內不停重複看到那個字），人會覺得那個字變的很陌生，認為那個&rdquo;文字&ldquo;是由一堆沒有意義的線條所組成的。而有時候這個現象甚至並不止於文字，有些時候 人也會對於眼前見到的人事物，感覺到失去了&rdquo;現實感&ldquo;。<br />\n製作單位裡有位工作人員笙井就被詢問了，願不願意嘗試這個實驗...<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4eQDuVK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4eQDuVK.png&h=2d15cab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n方法就如上述說的，非常的簡單，就是在鏡子前面，問著鏡子中的自己：你是誰？<br />\n <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BZEenx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BZEenx.png&h=f3adc475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼說真的是我一開始聽到也會覺得這實驗好像滿無聊的..<br />\n <br />\n不過被找來實驗的人只被要求了兩個星期，而且也告訴笙井這個實驗到最後是會讓人發瘋的，笙井也會感到害怕。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbRWgAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbRWgAX.png&h=015c1532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這種情況下除了問萬一出事了怎麼辦之外..當然也會問那我有什麼好處嚕...<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5ThLuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5ThLuA.png&h=28c88298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n就這樣..說好如果完成之後就可以拿到一筆賞金，就開始了30天的實驗！<br />\n笙井就開始了他的實驗之路....<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLfW020.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLfW020.png&h=e176acfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n就像做紀錄一樣，第一天像鏡頭說說話，我們要開始做這個實驗了唷!<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZqDuWp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZqDuWp.png&h=c85c8ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n第一天...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Js3xzn7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJs3xzn7.png&h=6107c3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n第三天<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH1GsJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH1GsJb.png&h=45f9dc45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n這個實驗進行到第一個星期左右，因為擔心笙井的狀況，就問問現在有什麼感覺嗎？<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LVsogG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LVsogG.png&h=b6fd822e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n笙井說絕的實驗還滿無聊的，希望可以快點結束。<br />\n <br />\n▼不過沒想到...笙井就暈倒了...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eiG7ogM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeiG7ogM.png&h=46e7e978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n▼詢問了當時的主任，主任說沒有什麼其他特別的地方，跟往常一樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmsRPWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmsRPWQ.png&h=abf3712d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n實驗進行到第10天<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ok8p9WU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOk8p9WU.png&h=a520f0da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n實驗進行到第15天<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRUpqvh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRUpqvh.png&h=dcd9fb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n實驗進行到第18天<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPewPXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPewPXb.png&h=2bb30cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n已經超過18天了，可以看到鏡子裡的笙井越來越奇怪...不過製作單位這時候還不知道影片裡的狀況，<br />\n <br />\n▼看到笙井的臉色跟氣色相當的不好...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d32uBCf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd32uBCf.png&h=1b522a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n▼天天吃泡麵不好的...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKYEYQE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKYEYQE.png&h=471f9a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n後來攝影的工作人員去接了通電話後回過頭來發現....<br />\n居然在啃泡麵碗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7E5soho.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7E5soho.png&h=634ccbba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n工作人員也勸了笙井如果不行就不要在做了，中止也沒關係的！<br />\n但...<br />\n <br />\n第25天....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOpwPXr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOpwPXr.png&h=d7182c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKiQ5vQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKiQ5vQ.png&h=1980fa96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n第27天....<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4ukJhz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4ukJhz.png&h=61e11d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n最後就讓大家...自己來看影片吧.......<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/65tenLd6y90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F65tenLd6y90&d=roOfpUtotHjLxRc6RQnC5BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=898e12fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/65tenLd6y90</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完個心寒一寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b925fae0e6844e2168eb9490e66f0a87c3eff711","tid":992087,"uid":169154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fa7886817f7da9395b9401c493560e611b6495","tid":992087,"uid":172570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19518ac1b8abab4a18560b22d50dc50bba1a2c4d","tid":992087,"uid":16613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49baf30d06363d5f17796531a7839ff579ebebe","tid":992087,"uid":14210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後嗰幾張好恐怖"},{"pid":"8172ad91a0306ae080dcabd36a55ae330c113912","tid":992087,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"小學已經睇過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7649af45deeb91b14b2eb4f5e9ac8e170ef1a36","tid":992087,"uid":81256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:11:25.000Z","msg":"要搵食就唔會咁架喇"},{"pid":"8124751fe33b78778aceb44b8686cb7a68456c42","tid":992087,"uid":227402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"主角應該做左爺爺 退埋休"},{"pid":"56aaec7b42766d9272e27c60fd36ff8a88c70f52","tid":992087,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af592453fcf7df3308f1e9cccbc4486f5d6e611a","tid":992087,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/语义饱和\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E9%A5%B1%E5%92%8C&d=roOfpUtotHjLxRc6RQnC5BFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=6c9fc900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/语义饱和</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n語義飽和的原理在於「注意力轉移」，當人眼對一個字盯了一段時間後，大腦會不由自主地就僅僅注意字的某一部分，從而使這個字喪失了整體感，繼而對這個字的讀音和意義的記憶也會變得模糊。[1]這種大腦的行為不是人為可以控制的，因為在盯著一個字看了太久之後，會自動引起神經活動的抑制，形成聯想阻斷。無論是中文還是英文，這種飽和阻斷現象均發生在字形到語義的聯接過程中。[2]因此，人先會對字音感到困惑，繼而失去對字意的聯想能力。"},{"pid":"09f9577bc8c97010e4a48ef5e7cbe99af255c9e4","tid":992087,"uid":130976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8124751fe33b78778aceb44b8686cb7a68456c42","tid":992087,"uid":227402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T02:12:17.000Z","msg":"主角應該做左爺爺 退埋休"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"主角還健在嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292b1d1e2018f907a705386cb7605101f0a40625","tid":992087,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"有冇咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪個個可以攞白卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cf000368f3715859e55aded9a03598f7da70dd","tid":992087,"uid":130976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"292b1d1e2018f907a705386cb7605101f0a40625","tid":992087,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"有冇咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪個個可以攞白卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"要唔要試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c33e974ff3569c17ceea1d16de4dfcad5b828d","tid":992087,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80cf000368f3715859e55aded9a03598f7da70dd","tid":992087,"uid":130976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"292b1d1e2018f907a705386cb7605101f0a40625","tid":992087,"uid":225636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"有冇咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁咪個個可以攞白卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"要唔要試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:22:40.000Z","msg":"咁有冇錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d8cbc5f76be0f89b291123a911d08a4532dcb5","tid":992087,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"傻閪日本狗 中二到極點 唔怪得我地中國屌打班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7f6839b5adef62fb2d87020911fa8ebf8de0bc","tid":992087,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"假撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cce97260a05bb07c768b4cdf715ca1345c48080","tid":992087,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"對住塊鏡刷牙 刷撚咗十鳩幾年"},{"pid":"095a542ab9c46ca7cf960e75cab0a3a8f7611d5e","tid":992087,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"阿爺 我係你個孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ff8ce034839e083fa95b386e49655d5c049b07","tid":992087,"uid":130976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cce97260a05bb07c768b4cdf715ca1345c48080","tid":992087,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"對住塊鏡刷牙 刷撚咗十鳩幾年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"有冇問自己係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2627869f00c00bcefb72ad642340f7d17e8ddc35","tid":992087,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"真係有恐怖野就唔駛加咁多特效，配樂，化妝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"